{"tid":1460013,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦monitor 開HDR雪花問題","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:40:37.000Z","uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c76dda8f23892acd3a5d8f59da8cd975d0f957cb","tid":1460013,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"最近入手左隻 AD27QD <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻mon 支援HDR 技術，咁開隻mon hunt黎試下。換黎係下面既問題...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mkJNppF3nwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmkJNppF3nwg&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y99VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=07707db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mkJNppF3nwg</a><br />\n<br />\n唔開hdr玩係完全冇問題，但係一開就係咁彈雪花出黎，玩玩下佢仲好似support唔到黑畫面load左陣（唔止彈出卓面有雪花）。隻game setting hdr 開咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試過打LOL情況都一樣有雪花<br />\n<br />\n當時setting: 1440p, 144hz, G-SYNC On, HDR On<br />\n<br />\n試過調到120hz 情況一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身用緊display port試過轉hdmi情況一樣。<br />\nCheck過線鬆緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電腦硬件：CPU i7-7700, GPU 1080ti<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打試過一樣既情況？有冇得解決定隻mon壞？買左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e25fe1f4b4b8f135694517c793e4c0efb3f1cc2","tid":1460013,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:46:32.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"546dc6c8d4942cef42c450adfe75d5b4a31b7c1b","tid":1460013,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:49:19.000Z","msg":"張卡"},{"pid":"b3898a0db190cd5b25be24692d3119141ad2ef0d","tid":1460013,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"546dc6c8d4942cef42c450adfe75d5b4a31b7c1b","tid":1460013,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike